Background of unix and Linux and flavor of linux
=================================================
in 1950 > communication was unidirection

Scintist developed UNICS software[written in B and low level programming language] to convert unidirection communication to bi-direction

With the help UNICS they have written a new programming language[rewrite B] they have given the name C programming.

with C they have rewritten UNICS for user purpose known as UNIX

Unix is a base operating system, we need to install application in top of unix to intract with it that is reffered as Linux

Linux= Unix + application

Now, their are multiple IT companies created their own Linux environment

1) ubuntu
2) Fadora
3) Centos
4) IBM-i
5) Redhat

