Problem with application deployment
===================================
1) Server is temporary, and it can be down at any time.

2) Autoscalling in not possible
       Example: 1 server support 100 user
                now, requirement is 10000 user > 100 similar server

Now, you need a enterprise solution to run your application.

1) Running application in data center.
======================================
Datacenter is a location where you would be having all the resources required for application[Compute, storage, networking and database]

If you want to setup datacenter it required very high cost, alternative is cloud


2) Running application in cloud.
================================
Running your application on someone else data center, and paying rent to them.


